data.description: ATTENTION...PRICE REDUCED!!! Take a look at this beautifully updated townhome here in Vinsanto. This home has an assumable FHA loan that anyone who qualifies for an FHA loan can take advantage of. This complex has 24 HR security Patrol. This lovely home offers 3 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, Each floor offers their own climate controls for your liking. floor is updated in natural laminate flooring. The bright kitchen offers SS appliances, granite countertops, and nice  space for your dining. The breakfast island is additional counter space/coffee bar! The 3rd floor offers two spacious   en-suites. The community offers a pool, playground, and full grass field to enjoy! Close to dining,shopping & 101HWY
